", "display_name": "Conquest", "value": 1}]}, {"name": "disable_invasions", "display_name": "Disable invasions", "description": "Disable invasions and prevent losing progress.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}, {"name": "faster_production", "display_name": "Faster production", "description": "Enable faster production and harvesting of resources.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}, {"name": "faster_unit_production", "display_name": "Faster unit production", "description": "Enable faster unit production.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}, {"name": "faster_conveyor", "display_name": "Faster conveyor", "description": "Enable faster conveyor.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}, {"name": "death_link", "display_name": "Death link", "description": "Enable death link.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": false}, {"name": "death_link_mode", "display_name": "Death link mode", "description": "Select the death link mode.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Choice", "default": 0, "choices": [{"name": "death_link_unit", "display_name": "Death Link Unit", "value": 0}, {"name": "death_link_core", "display_name": "Death Link Core", "value": 1}, {"name": "death_link_core_russian_roulette", "display_name": "Death Link Core Russian Roulette", "value": 2}]}, {"name": "military_level_tracking", "display_name": "Military level tracking", "description": "Ensure the player has enough military power to clear sectors. If turned off, the logic will consider that the player can clear every sector once they have the minimal requirement to land on that sector.", "randomizable": true, "visibility": 15, "type": "Toggle", "default": true}, {"name": "randomize_core_units_weapon", "display_name": "Randomize core units weapon", "description": "Will randomize core units weapon. Erekir 